{"title":"MAtery主题如何更改字体","uid":"431bbd5ce1d381584aa11e1699262df6","slug":"博客字体","date":"2021-07-13T15:09:04.000Z","updated":"2021-08-10T15:41:17.747Z","comments":true,"path":"api/articles/博客字体.json","keywords":null,"cover":"https://cdn.jsdelivr.net/gh/sky20681/sky20681/img/2.jpg","content":"<h2 id=\"麻溜的开始吧\"><a href=\"#麻溜的开始吧\" class=\"headerlink\" title=\"麻溜的开始吧\"></a><center><font color=\"#FF0000\">麻</font><font color=\"#D5002A\">溜</font><font color=\"#AB0054\">的</font><font color=\"#81007E\">开</font><font color=\"#5700A8\">始</font><font color=\"#2D00D2\">吧</font></h2><div class='tip warning'><p>默认的就好看，没事别瞎折腾<p></div>\n\n<div class='tip success'><p>准备工作<p></div>\n---\n\n<p>挑选一款心仪的字体<br>这里我挑了几款好看的<br><img src=\"https://cdn.jsdelivr.net/gh/sky20681/sky20681/2021/07/13/bokeziti/1.png\"><br>然后拿告白体做演示把🐶</p>\n<p><img src=\"https://cdn.jsdelivr.net/gh/sky20681/sky20681/2021/07/13/bokeziti/0.png\" alt=\"精选\"></p>\n<hr>\n<div class='tip success'><p>准备工作<p></div>\n\n<hr>\n<p>接着在hexo根目录的source中新建font文件夹，把下载好的ttf格式的字体放进去，以防万一，在根目录的网站_config.yml配置文件中，跳过这整个文件夹渲染，如下：</p>\n<p><img src=\"https://cdn.jsdelivr.net/gh/sky20681/sky20681/2021/07/13/bokeziti/skip.png\"></p>\n<hr>\n<div class='tip success'><p>新建CSS文件<p></div>\n\n\n<p>文字的格式需要CSS来调整，在matery主题/source/css文件夹下新建一个diy.css文件</p>\n<p>放入如下代码：</p>\n<pre class=\"line-numbers language-none\"><code class=\"language-none\">&#x2F;* Here is your diy css styles. *&#x2F;\n&#x2F;* 自定义css存放处*&#x2F;\n@font-face &#123;    \n    font-family: &#39;myfont&#39;;    \n    src: url(&#39;https:&#x2F;&#x2F;cdn.jsdelivr.net&#x2F;gh&#x2F;sky20681&#x2F;sky20681&#x2F;font&#x2F;Aa望江南.ttf&#39;),\n    url(&#39;https:&#x2F;&#x2F;cdn.jsdelivr.net&#x2F;gh&#x2F;sky20681&#x2F;sky20681&#x2F;font&#x2F;告白体.ttf&#39;),\n    url(&#39;https:&#x2F;&#x2F;cdn.jsdelivr.net&#x2F;gh&#x2F;sky20681&#x2F;sky20681&#x2F;font&#x2F;Aa初吻.ttf&#39;),\n    url(&#39;https:&#x2F;&#x2F;cdn.jsdelivr.net&#x2F;gh&#x2F;sky20681&#x2F;sky20681&#x2F;font&#x2F;Aa奶糖初恋体.ttf&#39;),\n    url(&#39;https:&#x2F;&#x2F;cdn.jsdelivr.net&#x2F;gh&#x2F;sky20681&#x2F;sky20681&#x2F;font&#x2F;Aa甜茶.ttf&#39;);\n &#125;\n \n body&#123;\n     font-family: &#39;myfont&#39; ;\n &#125;\n\n .diyfont&#123;\n    font-family: &#39;myfont&#39;;\n&#125;<span aria-hidden=\"true\" class=\"line-numbers-rows\"><span></span><span></span><span></span><span></span><span></span><span></span><span></span><span></span><span></span><span></span><span></span><span></span><span></span><span></span><span></span><span></span><span></span><span></span></span></code></pre>\n<p>当然啦，这里几款字体的下载链接如下：</p>\n<p><a href=\"https://cdn.jsdelivr.net/gh/sky20681/sky20681/font/Aa%E6%9C%9B%E6%B1%9F%E5%8D%97.ttf\">https://cdn.jsdelivr.net/gh/sky20681/sky20681/font/Aa望江南.ttf</a></p>\n<p><a href=\"https://cdn.jsdelivr.net/gh/sky20681/sky20681/font/%E5%91%8A%E7%99%BD%E4%BD%93.ttf\">https://cdn.jsdelivr.net/gh/sky20681/sky20681/font/告白体.ttf</a></p>\n<p><a href=\"https://cdn.jsdelivr.net/gh/sky20681/sky20681/font/Aa%E5%88%9D%E5%90%BB.ttf\">https://cdn.jsdelivr.net/gh/sky20681/sky20681/font/Aa初吻.ttf</a></p>\n<p><a href=\"https://cdn.jsdelivr.net/gh/sky20681/sky20681/font/Aa%E5%A5%B6%E7%B3%96%E5%88%9D%E6%81%8B%E4%BD%93.ttf\">https://cdn.jsdelivr.net/gh/sky20681/sky20681/font/Aa奶糖初恋体.ttf</a></p>\n<p><a href=\"https://cdn.jsdelivr.net/gh/sky20681/sky20681/font/Aa%E7%94%9C%E8%8C%B6.ttf\">https://cdn.jsdelivr.net/gh/sky20681/sky20681/font/Aa甜茶.ttf</a></p>\n<p>TIPs：我是不支持字体有版权的，原因很简单！</p>\n<hr>\n<blockquote><span class=\"custom-blockquote-svg\"><svg width=\"24\" height=\"24\" viewBox=\"0 0 24 24\" fill=\"\" xmlns=\"http://www.w3.org/2000/svg\" data-reactroot=\"\">\n<path fill=\"\" d=\"M22 12C22 6.5 17.5 2 12 2C6.5 2 2 6.5 2 12C2 17.5 6.5 22 12 22C13.8 22 15.5 21.5 17 20.6L22 22L20.7 17C21.5 15.5 22 13.8 22 12Z\" undefined=\"1\"></path>\n<path fill=\"\" d=\"M15.97 11.5H16.04C17.12 11.5 18 12.38 18 13.47V13.53C18 14.62 17.12 15.5 16.03 15.5H15.96C14.88 15.5 14 14.62 14 13.53V13.46C14 12.38 14.88 11.5 15.97 11.5Z\" undefined=\"1\"></path>\n<path fill=\"\" d=\"M7.97 11.5H8.04C9.12 11.5 10 12.38 10 13.47V13.53C10 14.62 9.12 15.5 8.03 15.5H7.97C6.88 15.5 6 14.62 6 13.53V13.46C6 12.38 6.88 11.5 7.97 11.5Z\" undefined=\"1\"></path>\n<path stroke-linejoin=\"round\" stroke-linecap=\"round\" stroke-miterlimit=\"10\" stroke-width=\"2\" stroke=\"\" d=\"M17 8.5C15.23 8.97 14.07 10.84 14.01 13.27C14 13.33 14 13.4 14 13.47V13.5\"></path>\n<path stroke-linejoin=\"round\" stroke-linecap=\"round\" stroke-miterlimit=\"10\" stroke-width=\"2\" stroke=\"\" d=\"M9 8.5C7.23 8.97 6.07 10.84 6.01 13.27C6 13.33 6 13.4 6 13.47V13.5\"></path>\n<path stroke-linejoin=\"round\" stroke-linecap=\"round\" stroke-miterlimit=\"10\" stroke-width=\"2\" stroke=\"\" d=\"M15.97 11.5H16.04C17.12 11.5 18 12.38 18 13.47V13.53C18 14.62 17.12 15.5 16.03 15.5H15.96C14.88 15.5 14 14.62 14 13.53V13.46C14 12.38 14.88 11.5 15.97 11.5Z\"></path>\n<path stroke-linejoin=\"round\" stroke-linecap=\"round\" stroke-miterlimit=\"10\" stroke-width=\"2\" stroke=\"\" d=\"M7.97 11.5H8.04C9.12 11.5 10 12.38 10 13.47V13.53C10 14.62 9.12 15.5 8.03 15.5H7.97C6.88 15.5 6 14.62 6 13.53V13.46C6 12.38 6.88 11.5 7.97 11.5Z\"></path>\n</svg>\n</span><p>新建完CSS后，需要引用他</p></blockquote>\n<p>在/themes/matery/layout/_partial/head.ejs文件中插入引用，由于还没有远程部署，我们推导出它的http链接：</p>\n<pre class=\"line-numbers language-none\"><code class=\"language-none\">&lt;link rel&#x3D;&quot;stylesheet&quot; type&#x3D;&quot;text&#x2F;css&quot; href&#x3D;&quot;https:&#x2F;&#x2F;cdn.jsdelivr.net&#x2F;gh&#x2F;sky20681&#x2F;sky20681&#x2F;css&#x2F;diy.css&quot;&gt;<span aria-hidden=\"true\" class=\"line-numbers-rows\"><span></span></span></code></pre>\n\n<p>也可以部署一下，然后打开链接看能否正常显示</p>\n<blockquote><span class=\"custom-blockquote-svg\"><svg width=\"24\" height=\"24\" viewBox=\"0 0 24 24\" fill=\"\" xmlns=\"http://www.w3.org/2000/svg\" data-reactroot=\"\">\n<path fill=\"\" d=\"M22 12C22 6.5 17.5 2 12 2C6.5 2 2 6.5 2 12C2 17.5 6.5 22 12 22C13.8 22 15.5 21.5 17 20.6L22 22L20.7 17C21.5 15.5 22 13.8 22 12Z\" undefined=\"1\"></path>\n<path fill=\"\" d=\"M15.97 11.5H16.04C17.12 11.5 18 12.38 18 13.47V13.53C18 14.62 17.12 15.5 16.03 15.5H15.96C14.88 15.5 14 14.62 14 13.53V13.46C14 12.38 14.88 11.5 15.97 11.5Z\" undefined=\"1\"></path>\n<path fill=\"\" d=\"M7.97 11.5H8.04C9.12 11.5 10 12.38 10 13.47V13.53C10 14.62 9.12 15.5 8.03 15.5H7.97C6.88 15.5 6 14.62 6 13.53V13.46C6 12.38 6.88 11.5 7.97 11.5Z\" undefined=\"1\"></path>\n<path stroke-linejoin=\"round\" stroke-linecap=\"round\" stroke-miterlimit=\"10\" stroke-width=\"2\" stroke=\"\" d=\"M17 8.5C15.23 8.97 14.07 10.84 14.01 13.27C14 13.33 14 13.4 14 13.47V13.5\"></path>\n<path stroke-linejoin=\"round\" stroke-linecap=\"round\" stroke-miterlimit=\"10\" stroke-width=\"2\" stroke=\"\" d=\"M9 8.5C7.23 8.97 6.07 10.84 6.01 13.27C6 13.33 6 13.4 6 13.47V13.5\"></path>\n<path stroke-linejoin=\"round\" stroke-linecap=\"round\" stroke-miterlimit=\"10\" stroke-width=\"2\" stroke=\"\" d=\"M15.97 11.5H16.04C17.12 11.5 18 12.38 18 13.47V13.53C18 14.62 17.12 15.5 16.03 15.5H15.96C14.88 15.5 14 14.62 14 13.53V13.46C14 12.38 14.88 11.5 15.97 11.5Z\"></path>\n<path stroke-linejoin=\"round\" stroke-linecap=\"round\" stroke-miterlimit=\"10\" stroke-width=\"2\" stroke=\"\" d=\"M7.97 11.5H8.04C9.12 11.5 10 12.38 10 13.47V13.53C10 14.62 9.12 15.5 8.03 15.5H7.97C6.88 15.5 6 14.62 6 13.53V13.46C6 12.38 6.88 11.5 7.97 11.5Z\"></path>\n</svg>\n</span><p>引用完后，需要更改生成样式</p></blockquote>\n<p>在themes/matery/中，查找font-family参数</p>\n<p>更改后面的值为diyfont，如图：</p>\n<p><img src=\"https://cdn.jsdelivr.net/gh/sky20681/sky20681/2021/07/13/bokeziti/diyfont.png\"></p>\n<div class='tip success'><p>基本完成<p></div>\n\n\n\n<p>最后，hexo cl<br>hexo g<br>hexo deploy<br>把需要部署的资源全部上传</p>\n<p>打开链接测试链接的准确性</p>\n<p>不出意外，推送后，打开网站并没有什么改变<br>这是因为CDN缓存的神奇</p>\n<p>这时候，需要注销掉CDN缓存,在本地查看效果</p>\n<pre class=\"line-numbers language-none\"><code class=\"language-none\"># CDN访问加速 \n# 第一次使用本功能，一定要先配置url，再&#96;hexo cl &amp;&amp; hexo g &amp;&amp; hexo d&#96;部署到GitHub的仓库，注意！必须是GitHub的仓库！\n# 如果必须要使用国内的coding或者gitee，可以采用双部署，同时将网站部署到两个仓库（其中一个必须是GitHub的仓库）\n# URL配置规则（例子如下）： https:&#x2F;&#x2F;cdn.jsdelivr.net&#x2F;gh&#x2F;你的GitHub用户名&#x2F;你的仓库名\n# 如果想关闭此功能，将 url地址 注释或删除即可！\n#\n# 注：配置了此项，就代表着本地调试的时候，网站依然会去GitHub请求资源（原来的资源），本地调试的时候记得将 此项配置 注释或者删除掉\n# 更多关于访问速度优化，请查看：https:&#x2F;&#x2F;blog.sky03.cn&#x2F;posts&#x2F;42790.html\n# 注：jsdelivr可以自动帮你生成.min版的js和css，所以你在上面设置js及css路径中可以直接写.min.xxx<span aria-hidden=\"true\" class=\"line-numbers-rows\"><span></span><span></span><span></span><span></span><span></span><span></span><span></span><span></span><span></span></span></code></pre>\n\n<p>hexo s启动本地端口查看</p>\n<div class='tip success'><p>接着介绍更改字体大小<p></div>\n\n<p>edge浏览器按F12，点击这个图标后，到网页上点击文字，看是哪个参数在调控它的大小，手动修改数值到满意大小，然后到本地文件上修改,找到font-face参数，把后面的值改为myfont</p>\n<p><img src=\"https://cdn.jsdelivr.net/gh/sky20681/sky20681/2021/07/13/bokeziti/3.png\"></p>\n<p>tips:<br>VS code,按F1搜索MArkdown插件可以实时查看，不用再下载专用的markdown编辑器了</p>\n<p><img src=\"https://cdn.jsdelivr.net/gh/sky20681/sky20681/2021/07/13/bokeziti/4.png\"></p>\n<p><img src=\"https://cdn.jsdelivr.net/gh/sky20681/sky20681/2021/07/13/bokeziti/2.png\"></p>\n<div class='tip warning'><p>为什么一套code，不同浏览器加载出不同的字体!!!???🤔️🤔️<p></div>\n\n<p><img src=\"https://cdn.jsdelivr.net/gh/sky20681/sky20681/2021/07/13/bokeziti/5.png\"></p>\n","feature":true,"text":"麻溜的开始吧默认的就好看，没事别瞎折腾 准备工作 --- 挑选一款心仪的字体这里我挑了几款好看的然后拿告白体做演示把🐶 准备工作 接着在hexo根目录的source中新建font文件夹，把下载好的ttf格式的字体放进去，以防万一，在根目录的网站_config.yml配置文件中，跳...","link":"","photos":[],"count_time":{"symbolsCount":"2.7k","symbolsTime":"2 mins."},"categories":[{"name":"主题美化","slug":"主题美化","count":9,"path":"api/categories/主题美化.json"}],"tags":[{"name":"字体更改","slug":"字体更改","count":1,"path":"api/tags/字体更改.json"},{"name":"字体大小更改","slug":"字体大小更改","count":1,"path":"api/tags/字体大小更改.json"}],"toc":"<ol class=\"toc\"><li class=\"toc-item toc-level-2\"><a class=\"toc-link\" href=\"#%E9%BA%BB%E6%BA%9C%E7%9A%84%E5%BC%80%E5%A7%8B%E5%90%A7\"><span class=\"toc-text\">麻溜的开始吧</span></a></li></ol>","author":{"name":"花开","slug":"